summary: One of the things I love about how Liam plays Caleb is how massively undignified he always acts when he’s injured. I just enjoy...
body:
One of the things I love about how Liam plays Caleb is how massively undignified he always acts when he’s injured.

I just enjoy Liam’s commitment to having Caleb not be any traditional kind of “unflappable” or “cool.”
